    "title": {
      "rendered": "Why Nonprofit Fundraisers Should Give More Attention to Gen X Donors"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Donors-Facebook.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-17704\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Donors-Facebook-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Gen X Donors Facebook\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Donors-Facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Donors-Facebook.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Donors-Facebook.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Donors-Facebook.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Donors-Facebook.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>There is a lot of discussion in the nonprofit sector about Millennials (a.k.a. Gen Y) and Baby Boomers and a growing interest in <strong><a href=\"http://www.bethkanter.org/hey-nonprofit-here-comes-gen-z-donors/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Gen Z a.k.a. #Philanthrokids</a></strong>, but almost no analysis of\u00a0<strong><a href=\"http://content.time.com/time/covers/0,16641,19970609,00.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Generation X (aged 35-50 years)</a></strong>. As the first\u00a0generation to donate online and the generation that pioneered web design, email, blogging, and online advocacy, ignoring Gen X is a big mistake. As Gen X rebounds from the Great Recession, Gen Xers are entering their peak giving years and nonprofit fundraisers\u00a0would be wise to pay more attention to how they give and why.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2>1. Despite the fact that Gen X lost more\u00a0of its net worth during the Great Recession than other generations:</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/actually-its-generation-x-that-is-suffering-most-in-this-recession-2012-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17667\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/GEN-X-Recession.jpg?resize=600%2C437\" alt=\"GEN X Recession\" width=\"600\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/GEN-X-Recession.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/GEN-X-Recession.jpg?resize=300%2C218&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/actually-its-generation-x-that-is-suffering-most-in-this-recession-2012-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Business Insider</a></strong></p>\n<h2>2. Gen X gives generously to nonprofits &#8211; an average of $1,033.28 annually.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.abila.com/lpgs/donorengagementstudy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17669\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Gives.png?resize=600%2C146\" alt=\"Gen X Gives\" width=\"600\" height=\"146\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Gives.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Gives.png?resize=300%2C73&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www.abila.com/lpgs/donorengagementstudy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Abila</a></strong></p>\n<h2>\u00a03. Gen X volunteers more than other generations. In fact, 29.7% of Gen Xers\u00a0in the United States volunteer.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.volunteeringinamerica.gov/special/Generation-X\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17672\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Volunteers1.jpg?resize=600%2C477\" alt=\"Gen-X-Volunteers\" width=\"600\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Volunteers1.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Volunteers1.jpg?resize=300%2C238&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www.volunteeringinamerica.gov/special/Generation-X\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Corporation for National and Community Service</a></strong></p>\n<h2>4. Thus, nonprofits should give\u00a0special attention to their\u00a0Gen X volunteers since volunteers give twice as much as non-volunteers.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.volunteeringinamerica.gov/infographic.cfm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17674\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Volunteers-Give-More.png?resize=600%2C522\" alt=\"Volunteers Give More\" width=\"600\" height=\"522\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Volunteers-Give-More.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Volunteers-Give-More.png?resize=300%2C261&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.volunteeringinamerica.gov/special/Generation-X\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Corporation for National and Community Service</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">5. The Gen X Hispanic donor community gives more than other generations while the Gen X Asian and African American donor communities give more than Matures and Millennials, but less than Baby Boomers.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/diversity-in-giving-study\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17682\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Hispanics22.jpg?resize=600%2C372\" alt=\"Gen-X-Hispanics22\" width=\"600\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Hispanics22.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-Hispanics22.jpg?resize=300%2C186&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/diversity-in-giving-study\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Blackbaud</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/diversity-in-giving-study\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17684\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Asian-Giving.jpg?resize=600%2C378\" alt=\"Asian Giving\" width=\"600\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Asian-Giving.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Asian-Giving.jpg?resize=300%2C189&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/diversity-in-giving-study\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Blackbaud</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/diversity-in-giving-study\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17687\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/African-American-Giving.jpg?resize=600%2C386\" alt=\"African American Giving\" width=\"600\" height=\"386\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/African-American-Giving.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/African-American-Giving.jpg?resize=300%2C193&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/diversity-in-giving-study\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Blackbaud</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">6. In the post-Great Recession economy, the household income of Gen X is higher\u00a0than other generations.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.pewsocialtrends.org/2015/03/19/comparing-millennials-to-other-generations/#!16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17676\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/High-income-of-Gen-X.png?resize=600%2C414\" alt=\"High income of Gen X\" width=\"600\" height=\"414\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www.pewsocialtrends.org/2015/03/19/comparing-millennials-to-other-generations/#!16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pew Research Center</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">7. Gen X donates to animal rescue and protection, environment and conservation, and health causes more than other generations.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/generational-giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17692\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Causes-Gen-x-Cares-about.png?resize=600%2C356\" alt=\"Causes Gen x Cares about\" width=\"600\" height=\"356\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Causes-Gen-x-Cares-about.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Causes-Gen-x-Cares-about.png?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/generational-giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Blackbaud</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">8. Gen X donates more frequently than other generations.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/generational-giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17694\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-gives-most-often.png?resize=600%2C460\" alt=\"Gen X gives most often\" width=\"600\" height=\"460\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-gives-most-often.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-gives-most-often.png?resize=300%2C230&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/generational-giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Blackbaud</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Gen-X-gives-most-often.png\"><br />\n</a></p>\n<h2>9. Gen X participates in peer-to-peer fundraising campaigns more than other generations.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/generational-giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17696\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Causes-Gen-x-Cares-peer-to-peer.png?resize=600%2C389\" alt=\"Causes Gen x Cares peer to peer\" width=\"600\" height=\"389\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Causes-Gen-x-Cares-peer-to-peer.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Causes-Gen-x-Cares-peer-to-peer.png?resize=300%2C194&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/generational-giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Blackbaud</a></strong></p>\n<h2>10. Gen X is tech savvy and appreciates nonprofits that\u00a0embrace digital communications and fundraising &#8211; including mobile.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/generational-giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17698\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/how-to-stay-in-touch-with-gen-x.png?resize=600%2C258\" alt=\"how to stay in touch with gen x\" width=\"600\" height=\"258\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/how-to-stay-in-touch-with-gen-x.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/how-to-stay-in-touch-with-gen-x.png?resize=300%2C129&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/generational-giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Blackbaud</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/generational-giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17699\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/social-media-generation-x.png?resize=600%2C508\" alt=\"social media generation x\" width=\"600\" height=\"508\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/social-media-generation-x.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/social-media-generation-x.png?resize=300%2C254&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/generational-giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Blackbaud</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.pewinternet.org/2015/04/01/us-smartphone-use-in-2015/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17717\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/smartphone-ownership.png?resize=600%2C559\" alt=\"smartphone ownership\" width=\"600\" height=\"559\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/smartphone-ownership.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/smartphone-ownership.png?resize=300%2C279&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www.pewinternet.org/2015/04/01/us-smartphone-use-in-2015/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pew Research Center</a></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<table style=\"border-color: transparent; width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/social-and-mobile-media-webinars-for-nonprofits/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-17655\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/TWO.png?resize=299%2C167\" alt=\"TWO\" width=\"299\" height=\"167\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/social-and-mobile-media-training-for-nonprofits/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-17656\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/ONE.png?resize=299%2C167\" alt=\"ONE\" width=\"299\" height=\"167\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n",
